    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Awed by the beau--ty__ of thy vir-gin--i-ty and the re-splend-en-cy__ of thy great pu--ri-ty, the an-gel Gab-ri-el called out to thee thus, O The-o-to--kos: What__ wor-thy hymn of praise__ can I of--fer un--to thee? How shall I re-fer to__ thee? I am caught in be-wil-der-ment. And there-fore as com-mand--ed, I cry out: Maid--en full of grace, re-joice thou.\n\nMaid--en full of grace, re-joice thou.____"
    }
